<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two<rs type="material"> white marble</rs>  <rs type="objectType">frieze</rs> blocks: the first (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.685</measure> long) bears the mark <foreign lang="grc">ΑΑ</foreign>; the second (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.97</measure>) has <foreign lang="grc"><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Β</supplied>Α</foreign>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> in 3 lines on the fascia. The text began on a third, missing, block to the left.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>
<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.026-0.027</measure>. Star for stop.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0034" notAfter="0100" exact="none">Mid to late first century A.D.</date>
 (<rs type="criteria">prosopography</rs>, <rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>) or a descendant.</p>
</div>
